<div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
	 <h4 class="header">Fire Characteristics</h4>
	<div class="text">Fluvial processes such as flooding primarily maintain this alliance rather than fire. <i>Salix lemmonii </i>sprouts, recovering rapidly from damage (Zasada 1986).</div>
